Package xyz.rk0cc.jogu

package xyz.rk0cc.jogu

Java object of Git repository URL.

This library follows Git's supported protocol for locating remote repository:
  • Git protocol
  • HTTPS protocol
  • SSH protocol:
    • Traditional
    • Alternative
(Only 'File' protocol is not included in this package since it just crawling local package only and not recommended to uses)
Since:
1.0.0
See Also:
  • Official documentation about Git on server protocol
  • Class
    Description
    GitAltSSHRepositoryURL
    An alternative form of GitSSHRepositoryURL which omit protocol and completely incompatible address with URI.
    GitGitRepositoryURL
    An object of Git repository URL address which using git:// to crawl files.
    GitHttpsRepositoryURL
    An object of Git repository URL address which using https:// to crawl files.
    GitRepositoryURL
    An interface that indicating this object is referencing the location of remote Git repository.
    GitSSHRepositoryURL
    An object of Git repository URL address which using ssh:// with userinfo to crawl files.
    GitUserinfoRepositoryURL
    This interface allows GitRepositoryURL parsing userinfo in the URL.
    LegitURIFormat
    This interface of GitRepositoryURL is compatible with URI.
    UnknownGitRepositoryURLTypeException
    An exception throws from GitRepositoryURL parsers that has unexpected exception thrown due to invalid type of Git repository URL found.
